description: Erection of two buildings: Building A - part five/part six/part seven/part ten storeys for use as 164 residential units, two Class A1 retail/ Class A3 restaurant units and a street sweepers depot; Building B - rising in stages from six storeys to fourteen storeys with tower feature for use as a 159 residential units (including 71 affordable units) and a Class A1 retail/ Class A3 restaurant unit.
